high_descs: Turn left, go to the side of the white table opposite the wall.
Take the large knife from the table.
Turn left, go to the trash can with the trash can in front of the table with the microwave.
Cut the apple on the table with the microwave.
Turn right, go straight, at the white table turn right, go to the fridge.
Put the knife on the top shelf of the bottom compartment of the fridge.
Turn around, go back to the trash can that is next to the table with the microwave.
Take a piece of the apple from the table.
Turn right, go straight, at the end of the white table on the left turn right. Go to the sink.
Put the piece of apple in the sink. Wash the apple. Take the apple from the sink.
Go left to the black stand to the left of the sink counter.
Put the apple on the lower left corner of the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean piece of apple on a stand.

high_descs: Move to the left and face the kitchen table.
Pick the yellow knife up off of the table.
Move to the left to face the microwave table.
Cut the apple on the table in three slices.
Turn around and go right to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the knife inside of it and shut the door.
Turn around to face the microwave table.
Pick up one of the slices of apple.
Turn around, go to the right, and face the sink.
Place the apple slice into the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and pick up the apple slice.
Move to the left to face the small black table.
Set the apple slice down on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Place one apple slice on to the small black table.
